Package: PEPPER
Title: PErsonalized Perturbation ProfilER
Version: 0.1
Author: Emre Guney and Joerg Menche
Maintainer: Emre Guney <emreguney@gmail.com>
Description: z-score based gene expression analysis for
    individual samples.
    Provides methods to get
    z-score matrix for a given GEO data set.
    The z-scores are calculated for each gene in each sample
    using the mean and sd over provided control samples.
Imports:
    Biobase,
    GEOquery
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Suggests:
    limma,
    affy,
    samr,
    preprocessCore,
    makecdfenv
License: TBA - potentially GPL
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1.9000
